gotta make a webclient or rar your client and upload it to mediafire or uppit, then open no-ip duc, then open server and client and log in and wait for ppl to join, but u gotta go on r-locus and make ur server up there to vote on and stuff

www.portforward.com, check firewalls are off and I advice not to use UTorrent.
